{"tid":1130471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山男子租車燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-04-29T05:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ba7c8ed8d041f8daf3d21e4e48b8248b3b7180","tid":1130471,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"今早(29日)8時18分，有途人行經馬鞍山村路時，發現一名年約60歲男子，昏迷一輛私家車的司機位上，由於昨日已見該車停泊在上址，感到事有蹺蹊報警。警方及救護員趕至，證實司機已氣絕身亡，並且在車廂內發現有燒過的木炭，相信他燒炭自殺，並且檢獲懷疑遺書，正聯絡其家人助查。 <br />\n<br />\n警方根據車牌資料追查，證實該車屬於一間租車公司，由事主早前租用。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=23fb8171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/mobile/bkn-20190429085115031-0429_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190429085115031-0429_00822_001.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=0c13c4c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/mobile/bkn-20190429085115031-0429_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"94714faff6787f27c5974b7716e7f60dd36f12a1","tid":1130471,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57e10543f967b8ae2ed5469e86e6a9cca2d69c17","tid":1130471,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:07:36.000Z","msg":"唔捱得"},{"pid":"a3a3dbc78bead04bf7a42c2732519669f210198e","tid":1130471,"uid":71768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:23.000Z","msg"